  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is an American style buffet with a beautiful spread of organic, local produce waiting for you when you wake up each morning.</p>
<p><strong>Summit Restaurant </strong>is fine dining for real foodies. This elegant restaurant is known for serving traditional recipes with a modern twist. All of the dishes are made using seasonal ingredients from the area, where possible. They also have a fantastic wine list, so you're sure to find the perfect accompaniment to your meal. </p>
<p><strong><span>Cliffhanger’s Grill </span></strong><span>has a</span> lively, warm atmosphere and overlooks the beautiful valley. They serve breakfast, lunch and dinner. The food here is rooted in local tradition and specialises in authentic Italian cuisine cooked in the charcoal oven.</p>
<p><strong>Boulder Bar </strong>is perfect for a good espresso in the morning and a tailor-made cocktail in the evening. If you're feeling peckish, they serve snacks here throughout the day including sandwiches, salads and pizzas. Open 8am to midnight.</p>
<p><strong>Champagnerie</strong> is a lovely champagne corner and the place to go for gourmet canapés accompanied by a glass of fizz.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
