  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Suites</strong> are 55m² and sleep up to three people. They each have two floors with floor-to-ceiling windows, a terrace, TV, minibar, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, safe, shower and hairdryer. The entry level has a lounge with a sofa bed and a bathroom and the first floor has a double bed and bathroom.</p>
<p><strong>Family Suites </strong>are available on request and have twin beds in the lounge area and a king-size bed on the first floor.</p>
<p>Suites can be booked for sole occupancy at a supplement, available on request.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
